{"id": "art-185", "label": "Art. 185", "title": "Art. 185", "slug": "art-185", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1024071622\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1978\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1024071622\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 185 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_652791418\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1977\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_652791418\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)În <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span>\nprev&#259;zute de <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> <span\nclass=SpellE>contabilit&#259;&#355;ii</span> nr. </span><span style='color:\n#1B1B1B'>82/1991</span><span style='color:black'>, republicat&#259;, cu\nmodific&#259;rile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> complet&#259;rile\nulterioare, consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>,\nrespectiv directoratul, este obligat s&#259; depun&#259; la <span class=SpellE>unit&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nteritoriale ale Ministerului <span class=SpellE>Finan&#355;elor</span>, în\nformat hârtie <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> în format electronic sau numai\nîn form&#259; electronic&#259;, purtând o semn&#259;tur&#259; electronic&#259;\ncalificat&#259; sau o semn&#259;tur&#259; electronic&#259; avansat&#259;\ncreat&#259; cu un certificat emis de o autoritate sau o <span class=SpellE>institu&#355;ie</span>\npublic&#259; din România, <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;iile</span> financiare\nanuale, raportul lor, raportul cenzorilor sau raportul auditorilor financiari,\ndup&#259; caz.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1364407854\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1976\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1364407854\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>,\nrespectiv directoratul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>-mam&#259;,\ndefinit&#259; astfel de reglement&#259;rile contabile aplicabile, este obligat\ns&#259; depun&#259; la <span class=SpellE>unit&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nteritoriale ale Ministerului <span class=SpellE>Finan&#355;elor</span> Publice\ncopii ale <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;iilor</span> financiare anuale\nconsolidate, prevederile alin. (1) urmând a fi aplicate în mod\ncorespunz&#259;tor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1206054012\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1975\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1206054012\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)În vederea efectu&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>publicit&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nlegale, Ministerul <span class=SpellE>Finan&#355;elor</span> Publice transmite,\nelectronic, la Oficiul <span class=SpellE>Na&#355;ional</span> al Registrului <span\nclass=SpellE>Comer&#355;ului</span> copii de pe urm&#259;toarele acte, în\nform&#259; electronic&#259;: <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;iile</span>\nfinanciare anuale <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, dup&#259; caz, <span\nclass=SpellE>situa&#355;iile</span> financiare anuale consolidate, raportul <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, dup&#259; caz, raportul consolidat al consiliului\nde <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>, respectiv al directoratului,\nraportul cenzorilor sau raportul auditorilor financiari, precum <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> indicatorii <span class=SpellE>economico</span>-financiari\nnecesari efectu&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>publicit&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nlegale. Publicitatea legal&#259; se realizeaz&#259; prin <span class=SpellE>men&#355;ionarea</span>\nîn registrul <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span> a depunerii <span\nclass=SpellE>situa&#355;iilor</span> financiare anuale, <span class=SpellE>înso&#355;ite</span>\nde raportul consiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>,\nrespectiv al directoratului, raportul cenzorilor sau raportul auditorilor\nfinanciari, precum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> prin publicarea\nindicatorilor <span class=SpellE>economico</span>-financiari <span\nclass=SpellE>extra&#351;i</span> din acestea.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_417716100\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1974\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_417716100\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)[textul din Art. 185, alin. (4) din titlul III,\ncapitolul IV, <span class=SpellE>sectiunea</span> VI a fost abrogat la\n04-nov-2020 de </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>Actul din Rectificare din\n2020</span><span style='color:black'>]</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1452665869\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1973\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1452665869\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)[textul din Art. 185, alin. (5) din titlul III,\ncapitolul IV, <span class=SpellE>sectiunea</span> VI a fost abrogat la\n04-nov-2020 de </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>Actul din Rectificare din\n2020</span><span style='color:black'>]</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_906402955\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1972\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_906402955\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Ministerul <span class=SpellE>Finan&#355;elor</span>\nPublice <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> Oficiul <span class=SpellE>Na&#355;ional</span>\nal Registrului <span class=SpellE>Comer&#355;ului</span> vor încheia un\nprotocol de colaborare, în vederea transmiterii, în format electronic, a\ncopiilor <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>informa&#355;iilor</span>\nprev&#259;zute la alin. (3).</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>*) De la data de 1 ianuarie 2011, <span\nclass=SpellE>situa&#355;iile</span> financiare anuale <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ndocumentele anexate acestora, prev&#259;zute la art. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>185</span><span style='color:black'> se depun numai la <span\nclass=SpellE>unit&#259;&#355;ile</span> teritoriale ale Ministerului <span\nclass=SpellE>Finan&#355;elor</span> Publice.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}